LISA DESJARDINS: Right.

18:16.529 --> 18:21.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Both of those men have their own
very complex
dynamics within their caucuses
or conferences.

18:21.067 --> 18:24.270 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We know that Hillary Clinton has
worked with
Mitch McConnell in the past.

18:24.303 --> 18:28.808 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
We understand it's a
relationship of respect,
not a particularly warm
relationship necessarily,

18:28.841 --> 18:32.812 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
vs. Mitch McConnell who did work
perhaps best
of all with Joe Biden.

18:32.845 --> 18:35.748 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's something she will have
to work on,
but there is a potential there.

18:35.781 --> 18:42.121 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Paul Ryan, I think, he is
someone who has
such difficult dynamics in his
own conference.

18:42.154 --> 18:46.125 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He has the far right, who
sometimes says they
will just jump ship on him.

18:46.158 --> 18:47.893 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
He's got moderates.

18:47.927 --> 18:50.396 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Those are things that the White
House under
Hillary Clinton is going to have
to be very

18:50.429 --> 18:51.897 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
tactical about.

18:51.931 --> 18:53.699 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They are strategists.

18:53.733 --> 18:56.669 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They're going to try to use that
to their
advantage, but it's difficult
for them, because

18:56.702 --> 19:00.439 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
sometimes Paul Ryan cannot make
the decisions
himself for his conference.

19:00.473 --> 19:05.711 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Amie, we have less
than 30 seconds
left, but how do you think a
President Hillary

19:05.745 --> 19:09.115 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
